snippet.title: A Fork in the Tale (1997) FMV PC game trailer
snippet.description: This game is a FMV game starring Rob Schneider. You play a character who saves a young woman's life and is transported to the dimension Eseveron. You spend the game trying to figure out what is going on and then thwarting the plans of an evil villain.
